{% assign page = 'careers' %}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Web Developer</title>

    {% include 'head' %}
  </head>
  
  <body onload="limespot.init()">
    {% include 'nav' %}
    
    <div class="ls-page ls-text-page">
      <div class="ls-section">
        <h2>Web Developer</h2>
        
        <div class="ls-sub-section text-left">
          <h3>Job Description</h3>
          <p>
            We are seeking a creative and highly skilled senior Web UI Developer to join the LimeSpot development team. The successful candidate should have a good understanding of Object Oriented concepts and a strong background in building responsive dynamic pages utilizing HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript, jQuery and AJAX communicating with RESTful web services.
          </p>
          <p>
            Working with our small team of experienced developers in a Scrum environment you will be responsible for creatively designing, developing and fine-tuning the features and web user interfaces of our product offerings within an SOA application platform. Designing and implementing reused libraries and modules to support the high level interactions and processes in an optimized, efficient and high-performing manner is an essential part of this job.
          </p>
          <h3>Responsibilities</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Develop a thorough understanding of our technology and the value it provides.</li>
            <li>Lead the design and development of the user interface for all of our product offerings.</li>
            <li>Work as part of the development team to ensure our product offerings are easy to use, visually appealing, and highly customizable for individual client branding.</li>
          </ul>
          <h3>Qualifications</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Good understanding of Object Oriented concepts.</li>
            <li>At least 5 years' experience building responsive dynamic pages utilizing HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript, jQuery and AJAX communicating with RESTful web services.</li>
            <li>Proven ability to work independently towards tight product delivery timelines.</li>
            <li>Experience working in an agile product development environment.</li>
          </ul>
          <h3>How To Apply</h3>
          <p>
            If you think you have skills that would match our needs, we'd like to hear from you. Please email your resume to <a href="mailto:careers@limespot.com">careers@limespot.com</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      {% include 'footer' %}
    </div>

    {% include 'endbody' %}
  </body>
</html>
